9 AN ACT TO AMEND THE LAW CONCERNING HIGHER EDUCATION;
10 TO AMEND THE LAW RELATED TO THE PROPERTY AND FINANCES
11 OF STATE INSTITUTIONS; TO AMEND THE LAW RELATED TO
